AssertionError: Bug#005. Expected result: Menu "My account" is displayed
Actual result: The trading platform page is opened

AssertionError: Bug#039. Expected result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are displayed ['Canada', 'Singapore', 'Gezondheidszorg', 'Telecommunicatie']
Actual result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are not displayed after selecting an item from the "Most traded" dropdown ['Canada', 'Singapore']

AssertionError: Bug#039. Expected result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are displayed ['Groot-Brittannië', 'Noorwegen', 'Spanje', 'Basismaterialen', 'Niet-cyclische consumptiegoederen & diensten']
Actual result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are not displayed after selecting an item from the "Most traded" dropdown ['Noorwegen', 'Spanje']
Failed: Bug № ??? 'Markets' menu not present for 'nl' language
AssertionError: Button [Accept all cookies] is not visible after 30 sec.

AssertionError: Bug#039. Expected result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are displayed ['Duitsland', 'Singapore', 'Zwitserland', 'Cyclische consumptiegoederen & diensten', "ETF's"]
Actual result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are not displayed after selecting an item from the "Most traded" dropdown ['Duitsland', 'Singapore', 'Zwitserland', "ETF's"]

AssertionError: Bug#039. Expected result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are displayed ['Italië', 'Noorwegen', 'Zwitserland', 'Gezondheidszorg', 'Technologie']
Actual result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are not displayed after selecting an item from the "Most traded" dropdown ['Nederland', 'Gezondheidszorg', 'Niet-cyclische consumptiegoederen & diensten']

AssertionError: Bug#039. Expected result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are displayed ['Groot-Brittannië', 'Hong Kong', 'Italië', 'Financiële dienstverlening', 'Gezondheidszorg']
Actual result: applied filters "Region/Sectors" are not displayed after selecting an item from the "Most traded" dropdown ['Groot-Brittannië']
